  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple, cute, and addictive pinball game. Challenge higher scores with the help and company of 100 adorable cats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Game Features:**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Simple yet addictive gameplay mechanics.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Interactive cat animations.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Cats can help you achieve higher scores.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Hand-drawn cute cats and retro game scenes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Over a hundred adorable cat sounds.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Helpful Tips:**  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click on a cat to pick it up. Once picked up, you can left or right-click to place the cat back down.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A simple, cute, and addictive pinball game. Challenge higher scores with the help and company of 100 adorable cats!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Game Features:**</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. Simple yet addictive gameplay mechanics.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Interactive cat animations.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. Cats can help you achieve higher scores.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. Hand-drawn cute cats and retro game scenes.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5. Over a hundred adorable cat sounds.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >**Helpful Tips:**  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Left-click on a cat to pick it up. Once picked up, you can left or right-click to place the cat back down.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
